<p>
  <span class="nym">Rhodri</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Middle Welsh</span> <i>rod</i> 'wheel; orb' + <span class="lang">Middle Welsh</span> <i>ri</i> 'king'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of an 8th C king of Gwynedd, a 9th C king of Gwynedd, and a 10th C king of Deheubarth.</p>
</div>
  
  


